        <updateDate>2021-09-21T11:14:15Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Illegal Alien NICS Alert Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the national instant criminal background check system to automatically notify U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement and relevant state and local law enforcement agencies when the system indicates that a prospective firearm transferee is illegally or unlawfully in the United States.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
