      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to require the national instant criminal background check system to notify U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement and the relevant State and local law enforcement agencies whenever information contained in the system indicates that an alien who is illegally or unlawfully in the United States attempted to receive a firearm.</title>
      </item>
